instance-variables.sText: Hi Gamer! Today's world is a place where women are given an equal place as men. But you know what? My family tested my baby's gender against law and now they want my baby girl to get killed even before she steps into the world. I am struggling to save my child. BUT BUT BUT i will not loose hope because i know i have the power to fight for my child....This is reality, a sad reality... Welcome to the game world where you can change something.
